Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================APART========================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虐海盗虐得正欢时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们与阿梅莉亚和杰路刚帝士久别重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们俩带来的大叔维瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然扮猪吃老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话又说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带来的奇怪战车炸飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟是只来路不明的谜样小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙、龙破斩？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 慢着慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戏份呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because  因为我是莉娜·因巴斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么东西搞的怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不知道是什么东西搞的怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才变成那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰 杰路刚帝士你也说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃就算让我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道是什么东西怎么搞的 这什么跟什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我啰里吧嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 莉娜 不要那么生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 请您继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 不要抛弃我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 无力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不准啰里吧嗦的 别没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就一件一件问过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个说要逮捕我的叫维瑟的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你们是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们塞伦王国收到鲁比那加尔德王国提出的正式请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们提供莉娜的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比那加尔德王国的正式请求？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是国际正式请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能随意拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与莉娜你们有深厚渊源的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被派来出差了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是以护卫的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从阿梅莉亚老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是国王代理比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他那里接到正式的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的因为是国家机密 所以没告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点上你们不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我这个普通的美少女天才魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和什么国家扯上关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉 莉娜的话 且不论好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起国家规模的事件总是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛伦议会是这么判断的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以赛伦皇家的立场来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于国家规模的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也希望能掌握一些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家规模的事件是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去的时候 不如毁灭掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把塞伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样真会引发国家规模的事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便把鲁比那加尔德王国也夷为平地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 慢着莉娜 别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 喂 不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了哦 莉娜·因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颠覆国家的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我维瑟·弗雷昂全都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了个麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是夸张的修辞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我可是听得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 总之先冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜·因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要逮捕你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你把来龙去脉给我好好说清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果理由能让我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说想逮捕我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我莉娜·因巴斯就束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是搜查官的主观臆测
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者只因为是我本人就逮捕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可就不客气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是从它开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的它…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指这个像乌龟一样的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确来说应该是它们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这鲁比那加尔德王国开发的魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接二连三地被破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 你想说这是我干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有证据怀疑她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是莉娜·因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是真希望我发飙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:29.50,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}黄昏よりも昏きもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:29.50,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}胜过黄昏之昏暗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.12,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}血の流れより紅きもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.12,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}凌驾鲜血之鲜红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里再来个龙破斩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拦着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对手是国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不得不战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这咒文就是根据之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这咒文…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指龙破斩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你们所见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的攻击魔法伤不了那魔导战车一分一毫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说能将其破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有龙破斩级别的咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能说就一定是我干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就跟新娘修行学的东西一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪儿的风俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不过是会用龙破斩就说我是犯人 谁吃你这套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便乱用这种高风险咒文的狂暴性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为旁人考虑的鲁莽作风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一笑带过的蛮不讲理态度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系这一切因素进行综合判断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能断定犯人就是莉娜·因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合了这么多案情证据也难怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到过去的行径
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说也的确是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫过去的行径啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么事 高里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论过多少年都一定会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你好好改过自新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会挂上黄色手绢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说些莫名其妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 这次事件中把那乌龟炸飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明就不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来的确如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为莉娜·因巴斯说的说服力实在太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就被骗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忘也别挑关键的地方忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只乌龟被炸飞的情景 你不是也看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你要说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时不是因为被Z1的攻击波及而昏过去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自满你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂阵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 再不快走太阳都要落山啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会使龙破斩的谜样小动物真的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得难以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被谜样小动物抢走戏份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记仇了记仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是怨念这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要彻底证明我的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们现在是去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是监察官维兹·弗雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求你们协助搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官这就去转告司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是戒备森严啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个要塞里集中了这么多兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非和邻国之间发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来正打算挑起事端呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了 司令官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 上面也说要协助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方会有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才忘记问了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才大叔说的事还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说发生了那个魔导战车连续被破坏的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要证明我的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住真凶是简单且唯一的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就让他带我们来下一个可能的目标这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人到底是为了什么而做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门即将打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…牛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是牛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设计的还真没品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方的人设计的东西就别挑剔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 暂时要看守一下这头牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻头彻尾中招了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都叫他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让他摆什么无聊的pose
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌 敌袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医务兵 司令官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了 快看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路和加梅利亚负责救助被波及的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去追那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小动物你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太胡来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它看上去也不是泛泛之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡来也好勉强也罢 无论如何都要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Van Rehl{\r}\N冰窟茑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这么嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Freeze Arrow{\r}\N冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊 很危险哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊 很危险的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你先来找事的吧 矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你先让我背黑锅的啊 你个小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是小动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是矮子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞 搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我都快被当成连续爆炸犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这关我啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你平日做人就不厚道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你平时多行不义才会遭此误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把你抓去绳之以法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没办法证明我的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有很多不得不做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这种地方被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说抱歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管你那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我用武力来逮你归案了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到就试试看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Dam Brass{\r}\N振动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意打得中才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 上窜下跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Diem Wing{\r}\N魔风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Windy Shield{\r}\N封气结界咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它相当熟悉战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那真的是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Bephis Bring{\r}\N地精道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用着不习惯的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近状态也太差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在失态…态…态…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夹着尾巴逃走 也就趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没长什么尾巴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下应该不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被魔导战车的爆炸波及 昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸犯的话 莉娜她们去追了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Dimilar Wind{\r}\N风波砾压破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Air Valm{\r}\N空断壁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Elmekia Lance{\r}\N烈闪枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小咒文的对抗 根本没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 灵巧性是对方占上风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也找不到使用强力咒文的破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 区区小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Freeze Rain{\r}\N魔结球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Ferrous Bleed{\r}\N白翼翔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的咒语是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下　马上就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是单纯召唤小鸟的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对付小动物比想象中还有效啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狼狈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底不过是小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就一直小动物小动物的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家又不是喜欢才变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 你也没大多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说什么大小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极薄？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极 薄…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 平…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你竟敢说出我的禁句
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是贫乳所以才叫你贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个从贫乳的国家里出来晒贫乳的贫乳王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你说…贫乳王？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说到这份上 那我也不能手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你似乎也会使用龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.75,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四界の闇を統べる王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.55,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝の欠片の縁にしたがい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.78,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝らすべての力もて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:08.61,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我にさらなる魔力を与えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.75,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统御四界黑暗之王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.55,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依循汝碎片之缘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.78,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由汝所有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:08.61,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予吾更强之魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔 魔力增强？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙居然会这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆风弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.64,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏よりも昏きもの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.65,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血の流れより紅きもの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.66,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時の流れに埋もれし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.58,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偉大なる汝の名において
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.82,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我ここに　闇に誓わん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.64,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜过黄昏之昏暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.65,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌驾鲜血之鲜红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.66,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐于时之洪流的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.58,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以汝之伟名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.82,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾于此向黑暗誓曰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你来这套…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.72,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等が前に立ち塞がりし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.58,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべての愚かなるものに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.74,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我と汝が力もて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.77,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等しく滅びを与えんことを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.72,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将阻挡吾等前路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.58,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切愚妄之物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.74,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合吾等之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.77,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予其平等的灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:47.11,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}元祖·龙破斩！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是龙破斩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是莉娜干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 你现在才爬出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍稍用了一下魔力增幅版的龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力增幅版…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点以为没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么光之剑会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会拿着这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然复制品只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复 复制品？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我试着造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光之剑以及那些魔导战车都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既拥有四界之玉 似乎也知道光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是高里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不过是普通的旅行魔导士和剑士而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当我是只普通的小动物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的小动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我必须阻止偷走魔导战车的人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷走？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜·因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你干的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那家伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 事情又变复杂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 普通的小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================ED========================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}{\pos(861,445)}{\fscx80\fs16}あめ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴れ渡る空から 落ちるとおり涙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴朗的空中落下雨泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}流れてゆく雲に 追いつけなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}漂浮的流云无从追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅立ちの先には 新しい出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅途前方是新的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}でも流されてるようで 落ち着かなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}但随波逐流的感觉令人不安
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}それでも この瞬間に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即便如此 这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全てが　終わる　訳じゃない そうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}并非一切都已结束 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あきれる程 悩み抜いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}摆脱那些琐碎的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出ない答え 今はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}未知的答案 现在已不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ほら本当は　あきらめていない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}看吧 其实你并没放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まだまだ行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}还能继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
